## Implementation Guide

### Data Sources

#### Device Information

- **Device ID*** (text):
  - **Validation**: Must be unique
  - **Format**: Typically follows pattern like "DASH-{SEQ}"
  - **Example**: DASH-001

- **Model*** (dropdown):
  - **API**: `GET /api/fleet/dashcams/models/` (if implemented)
  - **Alternative**: Hardcoded list of supported models
  - **Options**: DashPro X, DashMax S, etc.

- **Serial Number*** (text):
  - **Validation**: Must be unique
  - **Format**: Manufacturer-specific serial number
  - **Example**: DP-X2023-4567

- **Firmware Version** (text, read-only):
  - **Description**: Auto-detected from device if available
  - **Example**: v2.5.3

#### Vehicle & Installation

- **Vehicle*** (searchable dropdown):
  - **API**: `GET /api/fleet/vehicles/?has_dashcam=false`
  - **Display**: License plate, make, model
  - **Behavior**: When selected, auto-fills fleet operator

- **Fleet Operator*** (dropdown):
  - **API**: `GET /api/fleet/fleet-operators/`
  - **Pre-selection**: Based on selected vehicle
  - **Behavior**: Non-admin users have this pre-selected and disabled

- **Installation Date*** (date picker):
  - **Format**: YYYY-MM-DD
  - **Validation**: Valid date
  - **Default**: Current date

- **Installation Position** (dropdown):
  - **Options**: Front Windshield, Rear Windshield, Cabin
  - **Default**: Front Windshield

#### Connectivity

- **Connection Type*** (dropdown):
  - **Options**: 4G, WiFi, Ethernet
  - **Default**: 4G
  - **Behavior**: When "4G" selected, show SIM Card field

- **IP Address** (text):
  - **Validation**: Valid IP format if provided
  - **Description**: Only needed if using static IP
  - **Example**: 10.0.14.23

- **SIM Card** (dropdown):
  - **API**: `GET /api/fleet/sim-cards/?is_assigned=false`
  - **Display**: SIM ID, provider
  - **Visibility**: Only shown when Connection Type is "4G"

#### Recording Configuration

- **Recording Mode*** (dropdown):
  - **Options**: Continuous, Motion, Scheduled
  - **Default**: Continuous

- **Resolution*** (dropdown):
  - **Options**: 720p, 1080p, 1440p, 4K
  - **Default**: 1080p

- **Frame Rate*** (number):
  - **Options**: 15, 30, 60
  - **Default**: 30
  - **Unit**: fps (frames per second)

- **Quality*** (dropdown):
  - **Options**: Low, Medium, High
  - **Default**: High

- **Storage Capacity*** (number):
  - **Validation**: One of the standard storage sizes
  - **Options**: 32, 64, 128, 160, 256, 512
  - **Unit**: GB

- **Additional Features** (checkboxes):
  - **Night Vision**: Enhanced low-light recording
  - **Audio Recording**: Record audio with video
  - **Motion Detection**: Activate recording on motion
  - **Auto Upload**: Automatically upload footage
  - **GPS Tagging**: Include GPS coordinates
  - **Tamper Alert**: Notify if dashcam is tampered with

### Form Submission

- **API Endpoint**: `POST /api/fleet/dashcams/`
- **Request Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "device_id": "DASH-001",
    "model": "DashPro X",
    "serial_number": "DP-X2023-4567",
    "firmware_version": "v2.5.3",
